revision.text: '''Jaboca''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in the [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by having at least one empty plot and at least 600 points of bitter on the field. The [[Durin]] must be unlocked to unlock this berry. Various [[Farming Setups]] using Jaboca can be found [[Farming Setups#Roaming Pokémon Farm Setup|here]].
